<br>
I didn't expect that we'd have people come here that weren't interested in Roleplaying at all, to tell the truth. I had high hopes that everyone would Roleplay, and that the storyline in the game would be furthered.<br>
<br>
HOWEVER<br>
<br>
This STILL is the best server for roleplay in the game. I've learned so much more from the people here, Banegrivm included, about the storyline, and how to heighten my Roleplay and get better at it. ALOT of the people here do truely roleplay, and they understand enought not to take it IRL.<br>
<br>
