<br>
TLC was a bit of a challenge, but having researched my epic turned it into a long quest which I started back in my 20s. Nothing more fun then camping (solo)  the Blazing Elementals and Effretti in SolA while there where still Lightblue just to beat TLC.<br>
<br>
I will openly admit I dont roleplay all the time when playing, but when aproached by someone roleplaying its always nice to be able to have a good time RPing without worrying about people thinking you are nuts.<br>
<br>
Overall the population of this server is pretty good, nice, mature, courteus people. Though you will run into people now and again that you dont agree with or dislike, its going to happen anyplace, its just human, we are all different.<br>
<br>
Always a pleasure chatting with people, escpecially fellow magicians, any magicians out there with any questions feel free to toss me a tell, always a pleasure to help out when I can.<br>
